            "text_color": "#212121",
            "star_color": "#ff763d",
            "review_text": "\"I was skeptical about trying this and put it off for months. It seemed too good to be true but thought there's only one way to find out so I ordered some and I was not disappointed. Doesn't give me 100% coverage but a damn sight better than without!\"",
            "customer_name": "Carlos",
