            "card_background": "#ffffff",
            "card_border": "#d6d9e1",
            "text_color": "#212121",
            "star_color": "#ff763d",
            "review_text": "\"The product was incredibly easy to use and completely mess-free. It lasts significantly longer than any other product I’ve tried, which makes it even more impressive. comes with a built in applicator and is convenient to take with you wherever you go.\"",
            "customer_name": "Jake",
            "customer_age": "29"
          }
        },
        "review_CcgKbq": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/30.webp",
            "star_rating": 5,
            "card_background": "#ffffff",
            "card_border": "#d6d9e1",
            "text_color": "#212121",
            "star_color": "#ff763d",
            "review_text": "\"The Hairo filler arrived very quickly after placing the order, I ordered 3 pots for a great price. I use the filler most days on a thinning spot near the crown of my hair and the results are amazing. It’s easy to apply and isn’t messy to use\"",
            "customer_name": "David",
            "customer_age": "41"
          }
        },
        "review_NRLrJC": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/26.webp",
            "star_rating": 5,
            "card_background": "#ffffff",
            "card_border": "#d6d9e1",
            "text_color": "#212121",
            "star_color": "#ff763d",
            "review_text": "\"I genuinely found the hair density I wanted at my hairline. My wife just said I looked great, and some of my friends even regretted their hair transplant after trying this\"",
